tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 18, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jrp1665702556249.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrp1665702556249.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrp1665702556249.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jrp1665702556249\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determine the result when Uniface compares a numeric empty string to zero.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__topic_d142289e1_d142290e1_d142291e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__p_d142292e1_d142293e1_d142294e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__section_ivw_sdv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d152574e68\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__table_d17078e1_d17079e1_d17080e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Client assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__section_u52_vdv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d152574e116\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__ul_i3j_wdv_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__li_d50096e1_d50097e1_d50098e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—return TRUE when comparing a\n               numeric operand containing an empty string to zero; default </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__li_d50099e1_d50100e1_d50101e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—Return FALSE when comparing a\n               numeric operand containing an empty string to zero. <div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__note_j3j_wdv_jwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Use the setting only in assignment files for end-user applications.\n                  Do not set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code> in the\n                  assignment file for the Uniface IDE (<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span>) or in an\n                  assignment file for any other Uniface application.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__section_ds4_ydv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d152574e147\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__p_d142304e1_d142305e1_d142306e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO</span> determines\n            the value that is returned when Uniface compares an empty string (\" \") in a numeric\n            field to zero.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__p_d142307e1_d142308e1_d142309e1\">When this setting is omitted, Uniface behaves as if\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__section_u4t_12v_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d152574e167\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO</code></h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jrp1665702556249__pre_xtm_c2v_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO = FALSE</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529014\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529014\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 18, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determine the result when Uniface compares a numeric empty string to zero. $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO { = } 1 | 0 Defaults Assignment file: Client assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 1 Arguments 1 —return TRUE when comparing a numeric operand containing an empty string to zero; default 0 —Return FALSE when comparing a numeric operand containing an empty string to zero. CAUTION: Use the setting only in assignment files for end-user applications. Do not set $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO to FALSE in the assignment file for the Uniface IDE ( ide.asn ) or in an assignment file for any other Uniface application. Description $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO determines the value that is returned when Uniface compares an empty string (\" \") in a numeric field to zero. When this setting is omitted, Uniface behaves as if $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO is 1 . Example: $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO [SETTINGS] $NUM_NULL_CMP_ZERO = FALSE Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}